<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Password Expiry Reminder</title>
</head>
<!-- justin waz here -->
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;">
          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #2C3E50; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 24px; margin: 0;">
                {{ sub_email_branding.admin_team_name }}
              </h1>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Body -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px;">
              <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0;">
                Hullo <strong>{{ display_name }}</strong>,
              </p>

              <p style="font-size: 16px;">
                This is a friendly reminder that your <strong>{{ sub_email_branding.company_name }} domain password</strong> will expire in 
                <strong>{{ days_to_expire }} day{% if days_to_expire != 1 %}s{% endif %}</strong>.
                To avoid any disruption, please change your password as soon as possible by following the steps below:
              </p>

              <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; margin: 20px 0;" />

              <!-- Section 1 -->
              <h2 style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #2C3E50;">1. Change via Web Portal (Remote or On-Site)</h2>
              <ol style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Connect to {{ sub_email_branding.company_name }} VPN</strong> (if you’re off-site):
                  <p style="margin: 5px 0 10px 20px; word-break: break-all;">
                     Launch your OpenVPN client and connect to the {{ sub_email_branding.company_name }} network.
                  </p>
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Open a web browser</strong> and navigate to:
                  <p style="margin: 5px 0 10px 20px; word-break: break-all;">
                    <a href="{{ sub_email_branding.password_change_url }}?userName={{ samaccountname }}" style="color: #2980B9;">
                      {{ sub_email_branding.password_change_url }}?userName={{ samaccountname }}
                    </a>
                  </p>
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Enter your current password</strong> when prompted, then choose a new password that meets our requirements.
                </li>
              </ol>

              <!-- Section 2 -->
              <h2 style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #2C3E50;">2. Change on a Windows PC (On-Site Only)</h2>
              <ol style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Log in</strong> to your Windows workstation as usual.
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Press Ctrl + Alt + Del</strong> and click <em>“Change Password”</em>.
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Enter your old password</strong> in the “Current Password” field.
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Type a new password</strong> (see requirements below) and confirm.
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Click OK</strong> to finish, then return to your desktop.
                </li>
              </ol>

              <!-- Section 3 -->
              <h2 style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #2C3E50;">3. Change on macOS/Linux (On-Site Only)</h2>
              <ol style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Log in</strong> to your computer as usual (connected to the corporate LAN).
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Realize</strong> that it won't help your situation, potentially weep.
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  <strong>Go back</strong> and use the <strong>Web Portal</strong> method instead.
                </li>                
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                  If you have <strong>Jumpbox access</strong>, you could always try using that instead (using Method 1).
                </li>
              </ol>

              <!-- Section 4: Requirements -->
              <h2 style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #2C3E50;">4. Password Requirements</h2>
              <ul style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Length:</strong> At least 8 characters</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
                  <strong>Character Groups:</strong> Must include at least three of:
                  <ul style="margin: 5px 0 5px 20px;">
                    <li>Uppercase letters (A–Z)</li>
                    <li>Lowercase letters (a–z)</li>
                    <li>Numbers (0–9)</li>
                    <li>Symbols (e.g. <code>! @ # $ % ^ &amp; *</code>)</li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>History:</strong> Cannot match any of your last 24 passwords</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Username Exclusion:</strong> Cannot contain sequences of three or more characters from your username</li>
                <li><strong>Frequency:</strong> Cannot change your password more than once in a 24-hour period</li>
              </ul>

              <p style="font-size: 16px;">
                If you have any questions or run into issues, please contact {{ sub_email_branding.admin_team_name }} at
                <a href="mailto:{{ sub_email_branding.admin_email }}" style="color: #2980B9;">{{ sub_email_branding.admin_email }}</a>.
              </p>

              <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 0;">
                Thank you,<br />
                <strong>{{ sub_email_branding.admin_person_title }}</strong><br />
                <a href="mailto:{{ sub_email_branding.admin_email }}" style="color: #2980B9;">{{ sub_email_branding.admin_email }}</a><br />
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #ecf0f1; text-align: center; padding: 12px; font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
              &copy; {{ lookup('pipe','date +%Y') }} {{ sub_email_branding.company_brand }} — All rights reserved.
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
